OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,FPatients in Wales who are being
OL,7,Ftreated in hospital corridors are
OL,8,Fexperiencing "absolutely shocking"
OL,9,Fconditions, according to the nurses'
OL,10,Funion which has declared a "national
OL,11,Femergency" in the NHS, warning that
OL,12,Fpatients are dying in hospital
OL,13,Fcorridors.
OL,15,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN) -
OL,16,Fthe UK's nursing union - revealed
OL,17,Fpatients are being left without access
OL,18,Fto oxygen and enduring intimate
OL,19,Fexaminations in inappropriate crowded
OL,20,Fareas.
