OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,FAt the start of the union's annual
OL,7,Fconference in Newport, acting general
OL,8,Fsecretary Professor Nicola Ranger will
OL,9,Fuse her keynote speech to declare a
OL,10,Fnational emergency, releasing a new
OL,11,Freport on clinical care in
OL,12,Finappropriate areas.
OL,14,FThe RCN is calling for mandatory
OL,15,Freporting of patients cared for in
OL,16,Fcorridors to show the extent of
OL,17,Fhospital overcrowding.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/17
