OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,FJackie Davies, chair of Royal College
OL,7,Fof Nursing Wales board, said: "Nearly
OL,8,Fhalf of our members have told us that
OL,9,Fthey intend to leave the profession.
OL,11,F"Another thing that our members are
OL,12,Ftelling us about is this corridor
OL,13,Fcare, absolutely shocking, patients on
OL,14,Ftrollies, but not just on trollies in
OL,15,FED, extra beds being placed in wards
OL,16,Fthat are already full to capacity,
OL,17,Fwith a nursing deficit so they still
OL,18,Faren't fully resourced each shift.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
