OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,F"And if you're an additional patient,
OL,7,Fthey call it 'boarding'. You don't
OL,8,Fhave any privacy or dignity, you don't
OL,9,Fhave curtains around you. You don't
OL,10,Feven have your own oxygen supply, a
OL,11,Fcupboard to put your belongings in.
OL,13,F"Half of the time these beds are
OL,14,Fplaced in front of fire escapes, or
OL,15,Fslap bang in the middle of other beds,
OL,16,Fso it's completely unacceptable."
