OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says it
OL,7,Frecognises that the NHS across the UK
OL,8,Fremains under pressure, and it is
OL,9,Finvesting #283million in the education
OL,10,Fand training of healthcare
OL,11,Fprofessionals in Wales this year.
OL,13,FPatients are regularly treated on
OL,14,Fchairs in corridors for extended
OL,15,Fperiods of time, sometimes days, said
OL,16,Fthe RCN.
OL,18,FA survey of almost 11,000 frontline
OL,19,Fnursing staff across the UK showed how
OL,20,Fwidespread the practice has become,
OL,21,Fsaid the RCN.
