OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,FWhen asked about their most recent
OL,7,Fshift, almost two in five respondents
OL,8,Freported delivering care in an
OL,9,Finappropriate area, such as a corridor.
OL,11,FAlmost seven in 10 said the care they
OL,12,Fdelivered in public compromised
OL,13,Fpatient privacy and dignity.
OL,15,FProf Ranger will tell the 3,000
OL,16,Fconference delegates that the
OL,17,Fsituation is a "tragedy" for the
OL,18,Fnursing profession".
