OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,F"Our once world-leading services are
OL,7,Ftreating patients in car parks and
OL,8,Fstore cupboards", she will say.
OL,10,F"The elderly are languishing on chairs
OL,11,Ffor hours on end and patients are
OL,12,Fdying in corridors.
OL,14,F"The horror of this situation cannot
OL,15,Fbe understated. It is a national
OL,16,Femergency for patient safety and today
OL,17,Fwe are raising the alarm.
OL,19,F"This is about honesty and
OL,20,Faccountability.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/17
