OL,3,CHospital patients enduring 'shocking'
OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,F"Care being delivered in front of a
OL,7,Ffire exit isn't care.
OL,9,F"Signing 'do not resuscitate' orders
OL,10,Fin a corridor isn't care.
OL,12,F"Receiving a cancer diagnosis in a
OL,13,Fpublic area isn't care. It's a
OL,14,Fnightmare for all involved.
OL,16,F"We need to call it out as nursing
OL,17,Fstaff, and health leaders and
OL,18,Fministers need to take responsibility."
