OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We recognise that the NHS across the
OL,8,FUK remains under pressure, and we are
OL,9,Fincredibly grateful to NHS staff for
OL,10,Fthe vital work they do.
OL,12,F"Despite the difficult financial
OL,13,Fsituation, we have sought to protect
OL,14,Fvital NHS services providing record
OL,15,Flevels of investment.
