OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives say they would
OL,7,Fboost staff numbers with a tuition fee
OL,8,Frefund.
OL,10,FWelsh Conservatives' shadow health
OL,11,Fminister Sam Rowlands MS said: "The
OL,12,FRCN are right to expect more from the
OL,13,FLabour Welsh Government, the only
OL,14,Fgovernment in the UK to have ever cut
OL,15,Fa health budget.
OL,17,F"After 25 years of underfunding,
OL,18,FLabour-run Wales has the longest NHS
OL,19,Fwaiting lists in the UK, putting
OL,20,Fserious pressure on nurses.
