OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives would enact a
OL,7,Fsubstantial workforce plan to boost
OL,8,Frecruitment and retention with a
OL,9,Ftuition fee refund at its heart to end
OL,10,Fthe crisis in the health service."
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru says it would ensure
OL,13,Fnurses have greater flexibility to
OL,14,Ftrain and improve work life balance.
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru health spokesperson Mabon
OL,17,Fap Gwynfor MS said: "The pressures
OL,18,Ffaced by nurses are immense.
