OL,4,Ccorridor care amid 'national emergency'
OL,6,F"Patient safety is at stake due to a
OL,7,Flack of resources. Widespread
OL,8,Fretention issues and rock bottom
OL,9,Fmorale is compromising the safe
OL,10,Fprovision of care. It is simply
OL,11,Funsustainable.
OL,13,F"The problems in our health service
OL,14,Frun deep. Nurses need greater
OL,15,Fflexibility in their contracts, to
OL,16,Fallow them to train during their
OL,17,Fworking hours and improve their work
OL,18,Flife balance, and a Plaid Cymru
OL,19,Fgovernment would ensure this as a
OL,20,Fminimum.
