OL,6,F"We would take immediate action to
OL,7,Faddress the problems in primary care
OL,8,Fby training and recruiting more
OL,9,Fdoctors and restoring the percentage
OL,10,Fof NHS spend to primary care, and we
OL,11,Fwould increase care workers pay by #1
OL,12,Fabove the real living wage meaning
OL,13,Fthat the average care worker in Wales
OL,14,Fwould receive #1,872 more a year,
OL,15,Fshowing that we value their work. The
OL,16,Fmessage is clear, if you care for our
OL,17,Floved ones then Plaid Cymru will care
OL,18,Ffor you."
